The Flash Bitcoin software operates as a specialized fork of the Bitcoin network, leveraging advanced scripting techniques to simulate Bitcoin transactions. These transactions are indistinguishable from genuine Bitcoin transfers at first glance, receiving full confirmation on the blockchain and remaining visible for up to 90 days before being flagged and removed by the system. This extended visibility provides ample time for users to explore the intricacies of blockchain technology, test wallet integrations, or simulate real-world scenarios without the need for actual funds.
